OL,3,CStarmer 'fighting for his career' amid
OL,4,C'chaos' at Westminster, John Swinney
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FJohn Swinney has contrasted his
OL,8,F"reliable, experienced" leadership in
OL,9,FScotland with the "absolute chaos" in
OL,10,FWestminster, where he said the Prime
OL,11,FMinister is "fighting to save his own
OL,12,Fcareer".
OL,14,FWith the Conservatives and the SNP
OL,15,Fcalling for a vote of confidence in
OL,16,FSir Keir Starmer over his decision to
OL,17,Fappoint Lord Peter Mandelson as the
OL,18,FUK's ambassador to the US, the
OL,19,FScottish First Minister said "the
OL,20,Fwhole Westminster Government has
OL,21,Fdescended into absolute chaos".
