OL,3,CStarmer 'fighting for his career' amid
OL,4,C'chaos' at Westminster, John Swinney
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FHe described Sir Keir as a "weak and
OL,8,Fdesperate Labour Prime Minister
OL,9,Ffighting to save his own career rather
OL,10,Fthan fighting for people in Scotland".
OL,12,FHe was speaking ahead of campaigning
OL,13,Fin Edinburgh for the Holyrood
OL,14,Felections in just over two weeks, with
OL,15,Fthe SNP leader bidding to be returned
OL,16,Fas Scotland's first minister.
OL,26,@oD@\OUrD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
