OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776819790
OL,3,CStarmer 'fighting for his career' amid
OL,4,C'chaos' at Westminster, John Swinney
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FMr Swinney said: "At a time when
OL,8,Fpeople are facing sky-high food costs,
OL,9,Fenergy bills and petrol prices, they
OL,10,Fneed a government that is focused on
OL,11,Ftaking action to support them.
OL,13,F"Instead, they have a Westminster
OL,14,Festablishment that is engulfed in
OL,15,Fscandal and asleep at the wheel."
OL,26,@oD@ROUuD@AOUwD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776819790
OL,3,CStarmer 'fighting for his career' amid
OL,4,C'chaos' at Westminster, John Swinney
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FHe added that "while Westminster
OL,8,Fstands by, the SNP will take action on
OL,9,Fthe cost of living ` with bold plans
OL,10,Fto bring down the cost of food in
OL,11,Fsupermarkets, cap bus fares at #2 and
OL,12,Fprovide more support to families with
OL,13,Fthe cost of childcare".
OL,15,FMr Swinney continued: "If am re-
OL,16,Felected as first minister, I will be
OL,17,Fthe reliable, experienced leader that
OL,18,Fpeople need during these tough times.
OL,26,@oD@OOUuD@VO]wD@WOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
