OL,3,CStarmer 'fighting for his career' amid
OL,4,C'chaos' at Westminster, John Swinney
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"I will take real action to support
OL,8,Fpeople, and will always put Scotland's
OL,9,Finterests first."
OL,11,FHe added that Scotland "will always be
OL,12,Fan afterthought" to Labour and and
OL,13,FConservative governments at
OL,14,FWestminster, where he said there is
OL,15,F"never-ending chaos".
