OL,3,CStarmer 'fighting for his career' amid
OL,4,C'chaos' at Westminster, John Swinney
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FMr Swinney said a majority for his
OL,8,Fparty at Holyrood would "unlock the
OL,9,Ffresh start of independence" with the
OL,10,FSNP leader having pledged to use such
OL,11,Fas a result to push for a second
OL,12,Freferendum.
